CASE
  WHEN LOWER(trim(olupmj)) = 'null'
  OR trim(olupmj) = ''
  OR trim(olupmj) = '0' THEN NULL
  ELSE (
    concat(
      substring(
        CAST(
          date_add(
            concat(
              substring(
                CAST(CAST(trim(olupmj) AS INT) + 1900000 as string),
                1,
                4
              ),
              '-01-01'
            ),
            CAST(
              substring(
                CAST(CAST(trim(olupmj) AS INT) + 1900000 AS string),
                5,
                8
              ) AS INT
            ) -1
          ) AS string
        ),
        1,
        10
      ),
      '',
      lpad(trim(oltday), 6, '0')
    ),
    "yyyy-MM-dd HHmmss"
  )
END
